            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cook the potatoes </strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces.</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiling water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> over a high heat and cook for 10-15 minutes or until fork-tender.</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, drain and return them to the pot.</p>\r\n<p>Re-boil a kettle.</p>",
